  "title": "BIM Modeller (Construction, Hospital Project)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Work closely with the team to troubleshoot issues, ensure timely delivery of models, and maintain accuracy in BIM documentation.</li>\n  <li>Ensure CAD and BIM standards are upheld, and workflows comply with company policies and project requirements.</li>\n  <li>Support project teams by managing RFIs, creating presentations using BIM models, and handling related project tasks.</li>\n  <li>Prepare and print drawings for production, create presentation materials, and participate in design and model reviews.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in Civil Engineering or equivalent.</li>\n  <li>At least 5 years of <strong>3D modelling </strong>and <strong>Autodesk Revit</strong> experience in <strong>Construction Industry.</strong></li>\n  <li>Proficient in <strong>AutoCAD, Civil 3D, 3dsMAX</strong></li>\n  <li>Able to understand building design drawings and architectural shop drawings.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p>\n<p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p>\n<p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p>\n<p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
